{"tid":2437114,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟點樣先可以忘記同ex經歷過既野","createTime":"2021-03-07T15:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T16:25:34.000Z","uid":164888,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bb680ac01f96cc92361006765161260825a2811c","tid":2437114,"uid":164888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:55:34.000Z","msg":"明明已經過咗幾年<br />\n但腦海入邊總會flashback 同佢既回憶<br />\n明明記得傷害得佢好深<br />\n但佢最後個句我仍然會等你<br />\n好似刻咗係我個心入邊咁<br />\n而家有個投緣既對象係面前<br />\n我都唔夠膽進一步發展<br />\n我好怕開始後會諗起個ex<br />\n投放唔到成個心俾新對象<br />\n已經試過幾次係咁<br />\n已經傷害咗幾個對象<br />\n唔想係咁輪迴<br />\n點解個思緒會咁混亂<br />\n真係控制唔到<br />\n以為塞滿每日個時間表可以好過d<br />\n但原來係唔work<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158d139e845c88e5126713471cfceaba7f06df31","tid":2437114,"uid":392196,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:57:06.000Z","msg":"打科興"},{"pid":"40b037328bf6f163134690bc490eb04e46cf1e72","tid":2437114,"uid":77320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"158d139e845c88e5126713471cfceaba7f06df31","tid":2437114,"uid":392196,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:57:06.000Z","msg":"打科興"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a9052a843ed0afd7109c832d94cde8f43d16d6","tid":2437114,"uid":21282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"158d139e845c88e5126713471cfceaba7f06df31","tid":2437114,"uid":392196,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:57:06.000Z","msg":"打科興"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:59:51.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"7f15114c4354aa89fd415a2b63cc36fbd45b1c43","tid":2437114,"uid":3553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:02:05.000Z","msg":"無，同你一樣，過咗六年有時都會想起<br />\n不過宜家好咗好多<br />\n對住佢都算心如止水"},{